YARD OWLS - #2) "BOWIE SPARKLEDUST"

"...my special HUMAN is offbeat and different, just like me..."
                               --- BOWIE

The second YARD OWL is here!! 
Meet "BOWIE SPARKLEDUST" a lonely space cadet from our first wave 3-D collection, by the original artist:
the one and only HP LOVEBUX!

Grab it and trade it away - let's  have fun and ejoy the ride as we take TEZOS to the MOON!

These are fun affordable collectibles so tell your friends grab each new release!
